# Build context excludes — node_modules and build outputs are regenerated in the image.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/coverage
packages/db/src/generated
# Deployment definitions are build inputs, not application source copied into deploy trees.
**/Dockerfile
docker-compose*.yml
docs
.git
.github
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.log
scratchpad
